description:
➤ Our Chinese Language Website - https://www.amazingfacts.org/chinese-resources

BREAKING NEWS FROM CHINA! God opened big doors to the world's largest group of souls hungry for truth. Working prayerfully for months with church leaders and local government officials, Amazing Facts conducted a full-scale, 15-part Bible prophecy outreach series in Wuxi, China! Day after day thousands came, and sat attentively with a notepad and with their Bibles open as Pastor Doug Batchelor preached everlasting Gospel to the masses. This miraculous, historic event is the first time a public religious series has been presented by a foreigner of any faith in this nation since 1959!

chapters.title: Prayer for the Work in China
